Study of the Percentage of Greenhouse Gas Emissions from Aviation in the EU-27 
Countries by Applying Multiple-Criteria Statistical Methods.

Andrejiová M(1), Grincova A(2), Marasová D(3).

Author information:
(1)Faculty of Mechanical Engineering, Technical University of Kosice, 042 00 
Kosice, Slovakia.
(2)Faculty of Electrical Engineering and Informatics, Technical University of 
Kosice, 042 00 Kosice, Slovakia.
(3)Faculty of Mining, Ecology, Process Control and Geotechnology, Technical 
