Ethnic Differences Among Acute Coronary Syndrome Patients in Israel.

Karkabi B(1), Zafrir B(1), Jaffe R(1), Shiran A(1), Jubran A(1), Adawi S(1), 
Ben-Dov N(1), Iakobishvili Z(2), Beigel R(3), Cohen M(4), Goldenberg I(3), 
Klempfner R(3), Flugelman MY(5), Rubinshtein R(1).

Author information:
(1)Department of Cardiovascular Medicine, Lady Davis Carmel Medical Center, 
Israel; Ruth and Bruce Rappaport Faculty of Medicine, Technion, Israel Institute 
of Technology, Haifa, Israel.
(2)Heart Institute, Holon Medical Center, Tel Aviv Jaffa District, Clalit Health 
Fund, Israel.
(3)The Heart Center, Chaim Sheba Medical Center, Tel Hashomer, Israel; The 
Sackler Faculty of Medicine, Tel Aviv University, Tel Aviv, Israel.
(4)The Heart Center, Chaim Sheba Medical Center, Tel Hashomer, Israel.
(5)Department of Cardiovascular Medicine, Lady Davis Carmel Medical Center, 
